@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ntlcrc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v2 - wp.sin((v2 + 0.72 - v1 + 0.90)))
    v2 = (v2 - v0)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.39) * (v1 + 0.82 + v2 + 0.73)) + 0.67)
    tmp = v2
    v0 = (((v1 + 0.81 / tmp + 0.57) - v1) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.86 + v0 + 0.44)))
    tmp = 0.67
    data[tid] = v0
